<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-5D0DF386-496B-4F1D-A323-318F94B4D58B" version="1" lang="en-US"?><concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-5D0DF386-496B-4F1D-A323-318F94B4D58B" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic concept)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c concept oceConcept-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">22 The function of the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Printhead Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA03 </compcodenr></comp></title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-34C6A3E5-E809-4139-80CC-275A8CCF9EDC"><p class="- topic/p ">How does the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Printhead Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 22PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> function ? 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Definition</ph></title><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Printhead Distribution PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 22PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> is a functional part of 05 Y motion system . 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The next picture shows the context of the PBA. 
</p><fig id="FIG_B573C22A724A4E129B2019AA69D2AD59" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2E91E0B5-DB33-4ACE-9581-EA3828E80AFA-low.png" id="IMAGE_7D2B0AA5F8E94386828B7D54D65F3300" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2E91E0B5-DB33-4ACE-9581-EA3828E80AFA-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_CDD990D0C3454219815FF395CE0C5217" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Block diagram and functional operation</title><p class="- topic/p ">The next picture shows a block diagram of the functions of the printhead distribution PBA. 
</p><fig id="GUID-0DD38CBA-D875-42B3-BBA4-A0925BC76B72" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D43B47E9-4572-4956-B838-9CA5ACC86B46-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D43B47E9-4572-4956-B838-9CA5ACC86B46-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">The printhead distribution PBA has the following main functions: 
</p><ul id="UL_289F0200B27D43738DA5A4D840C6C275" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_994CC40F771E490DB6263F474E617CF0" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Provide power to <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Carriage PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 05PBA07 </compcodenr></comp> via the FFC interface. (Flex Foil Cable) 
</p></li><li id="LI_6F62FC0FE77E4B09892DA2B8F386911A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Feed through/convert some sensor signals. 
</p></li><li id="LI_B8D6A0E5D1BA42AFA35AD883D9FE7968" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Generate +12V for use on the carriage PBA. 
</p></li><li id="LI_1439C65EAB664E7FBACA004654AF61B2" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Generate 49.5V present signal . 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "> . 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After power-on of the system, the printhead distribution PBA will provide a 49.5V, a 36V, a 24V and a 12V power to the carriage PBA. All these powers are transported via the FFCs between the printhead distribution PBA and carriage PBA. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">During printing, the carriage PBA will send 2 rulers and 1 home signal to the printhead distribution PBA. These analog signals are converted to digital on the printhead distribution PBA and are then send to the embedded control. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The 49.5V input power is monitored on the printhead distribution PBA, and a 49.5V_PRESENT signal is created for the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp>. 
</p></section><section id="SECTION_505547C4BC0F4F1B8B5A57A6892E53F5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Also see</title><ul id="UL_2B937589D07A4D968B51A1E088410D2B" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_792C31D4524A4E1BA753C86B0E67BF2A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="22COMP01" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-F9B91945-CB0C-4E4A-AFEB-0B62B0D1872C.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>22 The components of Power</xref> 
</p></li></ul></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-B4557947-F0AA-4402-B5B4-34B41260F60F.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Functional description</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
